[{"type":"info","header":"重要：所有命令在哪里跑","html":"<p>本 workshop 的所有 bash 命令都在 <strong>EC2 实例的 SSM Session Manager 终端</strong>中执行——不是你的本地电脑,不是 CloudShell,也不是 AWS 控制台。下面的步骤会带你连上这个终端。</p>"},{"type":"warning","header":"","html":"<p>如果 Connect 按钮为灰色不可点击，说明实例仍在初始化中（UserData 脚本大约需要 2-3 分钟完成）。等到实例 Status Check 显示 2/2 passed 后再重试。</p>"},{"type":"warning","header":"如果报 agentcore 或脚本找不到","html":"<p>说明 EC2 的初始化脚本还没跑完（通常需要 2-3 分钟）。等一两分钟后再试,或查看安装日志：</p><div class=\"CodeBlock-module_codeBlock__LKx5X CodeBlock-module_hasCopyAction__WMrpt\"><pre dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: black; font-family: var(--font-family-monospace-q47m7k, Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier Prime', Courier, 'Courier New', monospace); font-size: 13px; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; box-sizing: border-box;\"><code class=\"language-bash\" style=\"white-space: pre; color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><code style=\"color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; float: left; padding-right: var(--space-scaled-xl-gt502a, 24px);\"><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">1\n</span></code><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">sudo</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">tail</span><span> -20 /var/log/workshop-setup.log</span></code></pre><span class=\"awsui_root_xjuzf_11ym3_559 CodeBlock-module_copyAction__E7A8w\"><span class=\"awsui_trigger_xjuzf_11ym3_594\" id=\":r2o:\"><button class=\"CopyButton-module_styledButton__sS63U awsui_button_vjswe_1ufnn_157 awsui_variant-normal_vjswe_1ufnn_206 awsui_button-no-text_vjswe_1ufnn_601\" data-testid=\"copy-button\" aria-label=\"Copy content\" title=\"Copy content\" data-analytics-funnel-value=\"button:r2p:\" type=\"submit\" data-analytics-performance-mark=\"6-1782463380417-7619\"><span class=\"awsui_icon_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon-left_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon_h11ix_3ufhe_189 awsui_size-normal-mapped-height_h11ix_3ufhe_248 awsui_size-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_244 awsui_variant-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_320\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 5H5v10h10V5Z\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path><path d=\"M13 1H1v11\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path></svg></span></button></span></span></div><p>如果日志最后一行显示 \"Workshop EC2 setup complete\" 但 agentcore 还是找不到,跑一下 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">source /etc/profile.d/workshop.sh</code> 刷新 PATH。</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"","html":"<p>SSM Session Manager 连接不会超时（不像 CloudShell）。即使断开后重新连接，所有文件和安装内容都保存在 EC2 的 30GB 磁盘上。</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"选择你的路径","html":"<p><strong>路径 A:逐步手动操作（推荐,约 30 分钟）</strong></p><p>按 2.2 → 2.3 → 2.4 → 2.5 → 2.6 的顺序逐步执行。你会亲手创建知识库、配置 Gateway、挂载 Skills、编写 System Prompt、部署 Harness——理解每个组件的作用和它们怎么拼在一起。适合想深入理解 AgentCore 架构的人。</p><p><strong>路径 B:一键脚本（约 10 分钟）</strong></p><p>直接运行下面的命令,脚本会自动完成 Phase 2 的全部操作。你会跳过手动配置的过程,直接得到一个部署好的 Agent,然后从 Phase 3（首次对话）开始体验评估飞轮。适合时间有限或只想聚焦评估方法论的人。</p><div class=\"CodeBlock-module_codeBlock__LKx5X CodeBlock-module_hasCopyAction__WMrpt\"><pre dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: black; font-family: var(--font-family-monospace-q47m7k, Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier Prime', Courier, 'Courier New', monospace); font-size: 13px; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; box-sizing: border-box;\"><code class=\"language-bash\" style=\"white-space: pre; color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><code style=\"color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; float: left; padding-right: var(--space-scaled-xl-gt502a, 24px);\"><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">1\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">2\n</span></code><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">cd</span><span> ~/workshop\n</span><span></span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">bash</span><span> 01-create-kb.sh </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&amp;&amp;</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">bash</span><span> 02-create-gateway.sh </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&amp;&amp;</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">bash</span><span> 03-configure-skills.sh </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&amp;&amp;</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">bash</span><span> 04-deploy.sh </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&amp;&amp;</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">bash</span><span> 05-setup-memory.sh</span></code></pre><span class=\"awsui_root_xjuzf_11ym3_559 CodeBlock-module_copyAction__E7A8w\"><span class=\"awsui_trigger_xjuzf_11ym3_594\" id=\":r2v:\"><button class=\"CopyButton-module_styledButton__sS63U awsui_button_vjswe_1ufnn_157 awsui_variant-normal_vjswe_1ufnn_206 awsui_button-no-text_vjswe_1ufnn_601\" data-testid=\"copy-button\" aria-label=\"Copy content\" title=\"Copy content\" data-analytics-funnel-value=\"button:r30:\" type=\"submit\" data-analytics-performance-mark=\"7-1782463380419-2231\"><span class=\"awsui_icon_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon-left_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon_h11ix_3ufhe_189 awsui_size-normal-mapped-height_h11ix_3ufhe_248 awsui_size-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_244 awsui_variant-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_320\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 5H5v10h10V5Z\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path><path d=\"M13 1H1v11\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path></svg></span></button></span></span></div><p>跑完后直接跳到 <strong>Phase 3: 首次对话</strong>。</p>"}]